<html>

<head>
    <title>PALETTE U</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="assets/images/logo-transparent.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/landing.css">
</head>

<body class="landing-body">
    <header style="background-color: transparent;">
        <div style="width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end;">
            <a href="/login" style="text-decoration: none;">
                <button>LOGIN</button>
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="floating-shapes">
        <img src="assets/images/emotion/shape/yellow.svg" class="shape shape-yellow" alt="shape" data-target="concept">
        <img src="assets/images/emotion/shape/green.svg" class="shape shape-green" alt="shape" data-target="features">
        <img src="assets/images/emotion/shape/purple.svg" class="shape shape-purple" alt="shape" data-target="video-showcase">
        <img src="assets/images/emotion/shape/red.svg" class="shape shape-red" alt="shape" data-target="closing">
        <img src="assets/images/emotion/shape/blue.svg" class="shape shape-blue" alt="shape" data-target="gallery">
    </div>

    <div class="main-body default-content">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <h1>PALETTE</h1>
            <img src="assets/images/logo-transparent.png" alt="logo" class="logo">
        </div>
        <h3>A palette of emotions that captures your story and portraits you.</h3>
    </div>

    <div id="concept" class="content-section">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>CONCEPT</h2>
            <p>Emotions are the colors of our lives. Palette U transforms your intangible feelings into tangible, visual landscapes. By capturing your emotional journey, we help you understand your story better.</p>
            <p>It matters because self-reflection is the first step to growth. Seeing your emotions visualized helps you embrace them, not just feel them.</p>
            <footer>
                <p>&copy; 2025 Palette U. All rights reserved.</p>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="features" class="content-section">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <img src="assets/images/emotion/shape/red.svg" alt="Emotion Logging" class="feature-image">
                    <p><strong>Emotion Logging</strong> Simple, intuitive tracking of your daily moods.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <img src="assets/images/emotion/shape/yellow.svg" alt="Memory Islands" class="feature-image">
                    <p><strong>Memory Islands</strong> visual representations of your memories in 3D.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <img src="assets/images/home/train.svg" alt="Train of Thought" class="feature-image">
                    <p><strong>Train of Thought</strong> A journey through your past emotional states.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <img src="assets/images/emotion/shape/purple.svg" alt="Custom Models" class="feature-image">
                    <p><strong>Custom Models</strong> Personalize your world with unique 3D assets.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <footer>
                <p>&copy; 2025 Palette U. All rights reserved.</p>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="video-showcase" class="content-section">
        <div class="content-wrapper">

            <img src="assets/images/landing/1.jpg" alt="video showcase" class="video-showcase">

            <footer>
                <p>&copy; 2025 Palette U. All rights reserved.</p>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="gallery" class="content-section">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>Gallery</h2>
            <p>Explore the diverse emotional landscapes created by our community.</p>
            <div class="gallery-grid">
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="assets/images/landing/gallery/1.jpg" alt="Gallery Item 1" class="gallery-image">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="assets/images/landing/gallery/2.jpg" alt="Gallery Item 2" class="gallery-image">
                </div>
            </div>
            <footer>
                <p>&copy; 2025 Palette U. All rights reserved.</p>
            </footer>
        </div>
        
    </div>

    <div id="closing" class="content-section">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h2>Start Your Journey</h2>
            <p>Ready to paint your story?</p>
            <p>Created by Carol Yu. Dedicated to everyone navigating the complex waves of emotion.</p>
            <footer>
                <p>&copy; 2025 Palette U. All rights reserved.</p>
            </footer>
        </div>
        
    </div>

    <script src="js/landing.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
